title: Lou Malnati's with Jon Gabrus & Christine Nangle (LIVE)
itunes:title: Lou Malnati's with Jon Gabrus & Christine Nangle (LIVE)
description:
This week, Christine Nangle (The President Show, Inside Amy Schumer) and Jon Gabrus (Raised by TV, High & Mighty) join the 'boys to discuss a cornerstone of Chicago-style pizza: Lou Malnati's. Plus, a live edition of The Wiger Challenge.

Recorded live at the Logan Square Auditorium in Chicago, IL.

Want more Doughboys? Check out our Patreon!: https://patreon.com/doughboys
